This mod allows increasing the cargo size of transports, mining ships, auxiliaries and carriers (including DLCs).

There are three cargo size variants to choose from:

[list]
[*]Cargo size x2
[*]Cargo size x4
[*]Cargo size x10
[/list]
All ship sizes (S / M / L / XL) will be adjusted, for both NPC and player ships. 

Existing and new ships will receive the adjusted values.

