As optional downloads, you can choose ship types to adjust separately, which allows mixing cargo multipliers (Transport ships x2 and mining ships x10 for example).

Available ship type downloads:

[list]
[*]Mining Ships
[*]Transport Ships
[*]Auxiliaries
[*]Carriers
[/list]
